data.description: Welcome to this conveniently located ground level 2 bed, 1 bath, near the 128th St Park & Ride. Close to the vibrant Mill Creek Town Center w/its array of shops & dining options. Commuting is a breeze w/quick access to I-5, 405, & Hwy 99. The unit itself comes complete w/washer/dryer, approx. 1 year old, and new laminate flooring. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace & slide open the door to the south-facing covered patio, which offers a great space for outdoor grilling. The kitchen features a breakfast bar that opens to the dining area. Primary bedroom w/spacious walk-in closet for all your storage needs. As an added bonus, the property comes w/transferable Fidelity National Home Warranty for peace of mind.
